Docker --> Container Engine --> Deploy the microservices on the Containers

 
1. auto-scaling of containers
2. auto-healing of containers
3. auto-load balancing of incoming requests across available containers
4. auto-deployment (without downtime)
5. auto-scheduling/clustering


Container Orchestration Engine --> Kubernetes

Docker Inc. --> Docker Swarm


Kubernetes Objects
-------------------
1. Pods --> have the containers (99% --> 1 container - 1 pod)
2. Replica Set --> maintains a stable no. of replica pods
3. Deployment --> deployment activities without downtime
4. Services --> exposing the pods, loadbalancing across nodes
